"{\"uid\": \"aninews.in-news-world-europe-indias-upi-goes-live-at-galeries-lafayette-in-paris-eyes-paris-olympics-boost20240705040742\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Add ANI As A Trusted Source For Reliable Information  ANI |Updated:Jul 05, 2024 04:07IST  Paris [France], July 5 (ANI): India'sUnified Payments Interface(UPI) has expanded its footprint to the heart of Paris, with the flagship store ofGaleries LafayetteonHaussmann Boulevardnow acceptingUPIpayments.This landmark move is a step further in realising Prime Minister Narendra Modi's vision of globalisingUPI, which is an Indian instant payment system developed by the National Payments Corporation of India (NPCI) in 2016.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 519, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 90, \"end\": 95, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2259104564508397e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 114, \"end\": 117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_News_International\", \"score\": 0.7938616973977226, \"rank\": 0.2501387003892477, \"text\": \"ANI\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_News_International\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_News_International\"}, {\"begin\": 154, \"end\": 157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unified_Payments_Interface\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.579436026042953e-21, \"text\": \"UPI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unified_Payments_Interface\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unified_Payments_Interface\"}, {\"begin\": 202, \"end\": 207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2259104564508397e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 364, \"end\": 377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Narendra Modi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\"}, {\"begin\": 418, \"end\": 424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9311531827788221, \"rank\": 0.07393712057168468, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"On July 3, 2024, theUnified Payments Interface(UPI) became live at the flagship store of the world-renownedGaleries Lafayettein Haussmann, Paris.\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unified_Payments_Interface\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.579436026042953e-21, \"text\": \"UPI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unified_Payments_Interface\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unified_Payments_Interface\"}, {\"begin\": 648, \"end\": 657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haussmann's_renovation_of_Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.968057021089191e-20, \"text\": \"Haussmann\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haussmann's_renovation_of_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haussmann's_renovation_of_Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 659, \"end\": 664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2259104564508397e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This expands the acceptance ofUPIin Paris after a successful launch at the iconicEiffel Tower,\\\" read a press release by Indian Embassy in France.Ambassador of India to France and Principality of MonacoJawed AshraflaunchedUPIby live use at the store in the presence ofNicolas Houze, CEO ofGaleries Lafayette, and Alain Lacour, Chairman of Lyra Group.Recalling the success of theUPIlaunch at theEiffel Towerin January 2024 and the meeting hosted for potential merchants with NPCI International in February 2024, the Ambassador welcomed the quick conclusion of the agreement and arrangement between Lyra and NPCI for the launch ofUPIat the world-famousGaleries Lafayetteahead of the Paris Olympics starting July 26, 2024, which is expected to draw large number of Indian visitors.\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 1443, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 702, \"end\": 707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2259104564508397e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 786, \"end\": 800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2009_bombing_of_Indian_embassy_in_Kabul\", \"score\": 0.9999999933393156, \"rank\": 5.936126343976583e-09, \"text\": \"Indian Embassy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2009_bombing_of_Indian_embassy_in_Kabul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2009_bombing_of_Indian_embassy_in_Kabul\"}, {\"begin\": 825, \"end\": 830, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999996276497551, \"rank\": 2.813258258099375e-07, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 834, \"end\": 840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9601104671217044, \"rank\": 0.03570082484812949, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 984, \"end\": 990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lacour\", \"score\": 0.9999985754285405, \"rank\": 8.590576406534042e-07, \"text\": \"Lacour\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lacour\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lacour\"}, {\"begin\": 1004, \"end\": 1008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyra_Belacqua\", \"score\": 0.9999999759461392, \"rank\": 2.33226513141639e-08, \"text\": \"Lyra\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyra_Belacqua\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyra_Belacqua\"}, {\"begin\": 1139, \"end\": 1143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Payments_Corporation_of_India\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NPCI\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Payments_Corporation_of_India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Payments_Corporation_of_India\"}, {\"begin\": 1427, \"end\": 1433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9311531827788221, \"rank\": 0.07393712057168468, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ambassador recalled the first international launch ofUPIin Singapore in 2018 by Prime Minister of India, Narendra Modi, and expressed satisfaction at the international journey ofUPI,\\\" the release also said.He hoped that, in addition to quick, safe and efficient means of cross-border digital payments,UPIwill grow as a medium of cross-border remittances and eventually become the digital payment system in countries across the world, it added.As Paris gears up for the 2024 Olympics, this initiative aims to facilitate seamless transactions for a growing number of Indian visitors and underscoresUPI's evolving role as a global digital payment solution.\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 2097, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1503, \"end\": 1512, \"title\"